data.title: Consular reception
data.meta_description:
Reception of citizens
The reception of citizens on different consular issues is carried out by the Consular Department of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs:
Monday, Tuesday, Thursday and Friday, from 10:00 to 12:00.
Address: Government House # 2, Vazgen Sargsyan 3, Yerevan 0010, Republic of Armenia
Tel: +374 60 620508
